column4: UPDATE 2-OMERS tech fund raises C$260 million from Cisco  Bank of Montreal
column5: TORONTO  Aug 17 OMERS Ventures  one of Canada's biggest venture-capital firms  said on Monday it has raised about C$260 million ($200 million) for a second fund to invest mainly in early-stage technology companies.
